<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>To receive credit for previous college coursework from a regionally accredited institution, an Advanced Placement Exam (AP), College Level Examination Program (CLEP), and DANTES Subject Standardized Tests (DSST), official transcripts must be submitted for evaluation, and the registrar or dean of nursing &amp; health sciences must approve the credit for transfer.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.trinitycollegeqc.edu/Admissions/Transfer-Students.aspx" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
